# Agenda

Agenda is a simple API allowing consumers to schedule meeting on-line.

# Group User

Resource operations related to users in the API.


## Login [GET /user/login{?username,password}]

+ Parameter
    - username : `zhang3` (string, required) - User Name
    - password : `123` (required) - Password
    
+ Response 200
    
            {
                "success"
            }

## Register [POST /user/register{?username,password,email,phone}]

+ Parameter
    - username : `zhang3` (string, required) - User Name
    - password : `123` (required) - Password
    - email : `123@mail.com` (required)
    - phone : `12345678901` (required)

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username":"zhang3",
            "password":"zhang",
            "email":"zhang3@mail2.sysu.edu.cn",
            "phone":"1234567890"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "id": 1,
                "username":"zhang3",
                "password":"zhang",
                "email":"zhang3@mail2.sysu.edu.cn",
                "phone":"1234567890"
            }


## List all Users [GET /users/allusers]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id":1,
                "username":"zhang3",
                "password":"zhang",
                "email":"zhang3@mail2.sysu.edu.cn",
