## Delete Current User [DELETE /users/deleteuser{?password}]

+ Parameters
    - password : `pass` (string, required)

+ Response 200
    
            {
                "success"
            }

# Group Meetings

Resources related to meetings in the API.

## Create a meeting [POST /meetings/newmeeting{?title,currentUser,participators,start,end}]

+ Parameters
    - title : `title` (string, required)
    - currentUser: `user` (string, required)
    - participators : `user2` (string, required)
    - start : `2017-11-01T10:00` (string, required)
    - end : `2017-11-01T11:00` (string, required)

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title":"title",
            "participators":"user"
            "participators":["user2"],
            "start":"2017-11-01T10:00",
            "end":"2017-11-01T11:00"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "id":1,
                "title":"Meeting",
                "sponsor":"user1",
                "participators":["user2"],
                "start":"2017-11-01 10:00",
                "end":"2017-11-01 11:30"
            }

## list all meeting [GET /meetings/allmeetings]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id":1,
                "title":"Meeting1",
                "sponsor":"user1",
                "participators":["user2"],
                "start":"2017-11-01 10:00",
                "end":"2017-11-01 11:30"
            }, {
                "id":2,
                "title":"Meeting2",
                "sponsor":"user1",
                "participators":["user3"],
                "start":"2017-11-02 10:00",
                "end":"2017-11-02 11:30"
            }

## clear all meetings [DELETE /meetings/deletemeetings]

+ Response 200
    
            {
                "success"
            }